des: Tucker Toman grounds into a double play, second baseman Eddys Leonard to shortstop Ryan Kreidler to first baseman Quincy Nieporte. Rainer Nunez to 3rd. Josh Kasevich out at 2nd. Tucker Toman out at 1st.
